Common Emitter Amplifier
* Supply and bias
Vcc vcc 0 DC $VCC
Rb1 vcc base $RB1
Rb2 base 0 $RB2
Rc  vcc col $RC
Re  emit 0 $RE

* BJT
Q1 col base emit BC547

* Input signal (AC coupled)
Vin sig 0 SIN(0 $VAMP $FREQ)
Cin sig base $CIN
Cout col out $COUT
RL  out 0 $RL

.MODEL BC547 NPN(Is=1e-14 Bf=200 Vaf=100)

.OP
.TRAN $TSTEP $TEND

.SAVE $SAVE_VARS
.END